(
 '<h2>Instructions for  use of Alisia mailinglists</h2>'
 '<b>NB:</b> The commands listed below must be given in the subject of the message! They are NOT case-sensitive.<br>'
 '<ul><li>Send message with ‚çôcmd_subscribe‚çô to the list to subscribe sender''s email. You will be asked for confirmation.</li>'
 '<li>Send message with ‚çôcmd_unsubscribe‚çô to the list to unsubscribe immediately.</li>'
 '<li>Send message with ‚çôcmd_nomail‚çô to temporarily pause delivery without unsubscribing.</li>'
 '<li>Send message with ‚çôcmd_mail‚çô to resume delivery after a pause.</li></ul>'
 '<h3>Message archive</h3>'
 '<ul><li>Send a message with "‚çôcmd_listmsgs‚çô" to the list to receive a summary of the latest messages.</li>'
 '<li>Use "‚çôcmd_getmsgs‚çô {a}[-{b}]" to retrieve message(s) {a} (optionally up to {b}).</li></ul>'
 '<h3>Your data</h3>'
 '<ul><li>Send message with "‚çôcmd_getmydata‚çô" to the list to receive a copy of the data we have stored for your email address.</li>'
 '<li>Answer this msg with "‚çôcmd_setmydata‚çô" and return your edited record (name + alternative_email may be edited)</li>'
 '<li>Send message with "‚çôcmd_deleteme‚çô" to permanently delete all your personal data (GDPR Art. 17).'
 ' Your subscriber record will be removed and your sender information anonymised in the message archive.</li></ul>'
 '<h3>More</h3>'
 '<ul><li>Send message with "‚çôcmd_stats‚çô" to the list to retrieve current list statistics.</li>'
 '<li>Send message with "‚çôcmd_help‚çô" to get this help.</li></ul>'
)
